      <p>
        Starbloom retains all rights to its platform configuration methodologies, workflow templates,
        orchestration patterns, and documentation. Clients retain full ownership of their own
        operational data, custom workflow configurations developed post-deployment, and any
        proprietary business logic implemented on the platform.
      </p>
      <p>
        The Starbloom name, logo, and brand marks are the property of Starbloom Consulting LLC. The
        platform stack components (n8n, Docker, Ollama, Cloudflare Tunnel, etc.) are the property of
        their respective owners and are used under their respective open-source or commercial
        licenses.
      </p>

      <h2>7. Limitation of Liability</h2>
      <p>
        TO THE MAXIMUM EXTENT PERMITTED BY APPLICABLE LAW, STARBLOOM CONSULTING LLC SHALL NOT BE
