      <p>
        Either party may terminate a deployment agreement with 30 days written notice. Upon
        termination, the client retains all hardware, data, and local configurations. Starbloom will
        provide reasonable transition assistance as defined in the deployment agreement.
      </p>

      <h2>11. Governing Law</h2>
      <p>
        These Terms shall be governed by and construed in accordance with the laws of the State of
        Maryland, without regard to its conflict of law provisions. Any disputes arising under these
        Terms shall be resolved in the courts of Washington County, Maryland.
      </p>

