        with an updated effective date. Continued use of the website or platform after changes
        constitutes acceptance of the modified Terms.
      </p>

      <h2>13. Contact</h2>
      <p>
        For questions about these Terms of Service:
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li>Email: <a href="mailto:fletcher@starbloomconsulting.com">fletcher@starbloomconsulting.com</a></li>
        <li>Website: <a href="https://starbloomconsulting.com/contact">starbloomconsulting.com/contact</a></li>
